{
  "stem": "56.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we have to-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was-- our home became like a gathering place for all these young people who had, by then, either lost parents, or had parents who were sick, because almost everybody had someone very sick from malnutrition.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- and my father kept the family together like that, and kept the young people together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then-- let's see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Things started to happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We heard that on the other side of the ghetto, the Germans had what they called actions, that they were taking people off the streets.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We heard all kind of stories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my father used to say, no, it couldn't be.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why would they grab somebody off the street?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why wouldn't they say, if you want to work, register?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, he still didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then one day, there was a terrible, terrible edict that they gave out, and that was that all children under I think it was 14-- I'm not sure the age-- have to be delivered to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the children.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember all the mothers with little children came to our house, and they were saying to my father, please save us, save us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father said, there's nothing I can do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rybowski, then can we stay in your house?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They felt that whatever will happen to-- they said, whatever will happen to your family will happen to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father said, but-- but you can't all stay here with the children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's nothing I can do about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some friends of ours who had young children came from the other side of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was like they thought that my father can perform miracles.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
